 and stain-resistant and overall affordable price at $89.98, or $56 off its list price — that’s nearly 40% off its list price. Meanwhile, the gaming chair comes in six colors, including black, pink, red, blue (pictured above) and more. Amazon Homall S-Racer Gaming Chair Marked down to $102.24, or $147.75 off, at Amazon, the Homall S-Racer Gaming Chair is a very popular pick with gamers. The gaming chair has an excellent ergonomic design and phenomenal angles, thanks to its locking multi-tilt mechanism that adjusts from 90-to-180-degrees with ease — which is great for posture and comfort. It’s also very durable with premium polyurethane leather materials that stands up to everyday wear-and-tear. The chair comes with two support pillows for their head and lower back, while it’s easy to put together and lock into place. It comes in a wide range of color options too, including white (pictured above), blue, cyan, green and more. Amazon ReSpawn 110 Gaming Chair The ReSpawn 110 Gaming Chair, which goes for $127.49, or $22.50 off, at Amazon, features lumbar support with a wide seat, while it’s very sturdy and comfortable with a 135-degree recline. It’s made from polyurethane plastic and faux-leather seats. The gaming chair is even height-adjustable up to 33 inches, as it’s ideal for people who are over six feet tall. It comes in six colors, such as blue, green, fabric gray, red (pictured above) and more. Amazon GTPlayer Gaming Chair On sale for $125.99 (reg. $169.99) at Amazon, the GTPlayer Gaming Chair is comfortable, thanks to its retractable padded footrest, linkage armrests and memory foam head and lower back cushions that help prevent neck and back pain. It even comes with built-in dual Bluetooth 5.1 speakers with audio richness and clarity for an immersive surround sound gaming experience. The gaming chair comes in six colors: Green (pictured above), ivory, wine red and more. Amazon Dowinx Gaming Chair If he’s looking for comfort, the Dowinx Gaming Chair — which is discounted down to $125.69, or $44 off its list price — is made with high quality breathable polyurethane leather that prevents him from getting overly sweaty. It also has a clever airflow ventilation design. In fact, the chair comes with a massaging USB-powered lumbar pillow for additional relaxation and comfort when gaming. It comes in four colors: Black, black \u0026 white (pictured above), brown and gray. Want more? For more product recommendations, check out our roundups of the best over-ear headphones, wifi extenders, laptop deals and more. Get weekly rundowns straight to your inbox Sign Up",
